 drivers/pinctrl/airoha/pinctrl-an7581.c | 138 ++++++++++++------------
 drivers/pinctrl/airoha/pinctrl-an7583.c | 132 +++++++++++------------
 3 files changed, 167 insertions(+), 145 deletions(-)

